  "description": "<i>MineClone</i> is a clone of Windows's <i><a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?game=Minesweeper\">Minesweeper</a></i>, written in E language for Workbench 3.0 and upwards. It is totally system friendly and supports localisation, dynamic pen allocation and runs on any public screen.<br><br>To make life easy for the player, <i>MineClone</i> lets you freely specify the amount of bombs, the size of the minefield, a safe start function so you never hit a mine on your opening move and an automark function that marks all the trivial cases.",
